    "description": "The centrifugal blood pump must demonstrate hemolysis performance substantially equivalent to a predicate device as required under 21 CFR 870.3545. Computational model results must support the 510(k) submission by showing RH < 1 across the worst-case operating envelope, consistent with FDA guidance on the use of computational fluid dynamics in cardiovascular device submissions.",
    "source": "21 CFR 870.3545; FDA Guidance: Reporting of Computational Modeling Studies in Medical Device Submissions (2016)"
  },
